: 16px 0;">The core idea of a pyramid scheme is:</p><ol style=3D"list-style=
-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"> <li style=3D"margin-b=
ottom: 5px;">You recruit some members to invest some money in the scheme.</=
